Package com.vmware.esx.settings.hosts.software

The com.vmware.esx.settings.hosts.software package provides interfaces to manage desired software on a standalone host.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AddOn
    The AddOn interface provides methods to manage desired OEM add-on specification for a given standalone host.
    AddOnTypes
    The AddOn interface provides methods to manage desired OEM add-on specification for a given standalone host.
    BaseImage
    The BaseImage interface provides methods to manage desired ESX base image.
    BaseImageTypes
    The BaseImage interface provides methods to manage desired ESX base image.
    Commits
    The Commits interface provides methods to manage committed changes to desired software document.
    CommitsTypes
    The Commits interface provides methods to manage committed changes to desired software document.
    Compliance
    The Compliance interface provides methods to get compliance results for a standalone host.
    ComplianceTypes
    The Compliance interface provides methods to get compliance results for a standalone host.
    Components
    The Components interface provides methods to manage desired component specification for a standalone ESX host.
    ComponentsTypes
    The Components interface provides methods to manage desired component specification for a standalone ESX host.
    Drafts
    The Drafts interface provides methods to manage working copy of software documents.
    DraftsTypes
    The Drafts interface provides methods to manage working copy of software documents.
    EffectiveComponents
    The EffectiveComponents interface provides methods to get effective list of components.
    EffectiveComponentsTypes
    The EffectiveComponents interface provides methods to get effective list of components.
    Recommendations
    The Recommendations interface provides methods to manage the generation and retrieval of recommended image specs.
    RecommendationsTypes
    The Recommendations interface provides methods to manage the generation and retrieval of recommended image specs.
    RemovedComponents
    The RemovedComponents interface provides methods to manage removal of components in a software draft.
    RemovedComponentsTypes
    The RemovedComponents interface provides methods to manage removal of components in a software draft.
    Solutions
    The Solutions interface provides methods to manage desired software solution specifications for an ESX host.
    SolutionsTypes
    The Solutions interface provides methods to manage desired software solution specifications for an ESX host.
